00:53:19,576 --> 00:53:20,856
Oh, Yumi-san!

616
00:53:22,576 --> 00:53:26,536
Yumi-san: Kie-san! I miss you.

617
00:53:27,696 --> 00:53:29,296
Pheem: You can speak Japanese too?

618
00:53:29,576 --> 00:53:30,496
Just a little.

619
00:53:30,616 --> 00:53:33,776
That employee must have taught you well.

620
00:53:33,896 --> 00:53:34,896
Are you jealous?

621
00:53:36,296 --> 00:53:39,336
Pheem: If you think doing all this can make up for those cruel things…

